。\n昨天萬聖節不能一起參加，真抱歉呢。\n應該沒事吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"bye01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"episode199-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"嗯！\n我玩得很開心喔！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"episode199-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"這樣啊，那就太好了。\n我找來的幫手怎麼樣？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"episode199-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"是個非常帥氣的人喔！\n我都嚇了一跳呢，\n小綾竟然認識那麼棒的人！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"episode199-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"（啊，這個反應……\n里美琳，果然沒發現那個人就是薰小姐吧）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[